// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0310 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 31354611-6747-51db-932a-c2e99a358516

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*azure linux:3.0*" or process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
